ACTION_HANDLE_APP_REGISTER

static final java.lang.String ACTION_HANDLE_APP_REGISTER
Register the third-party app to WeChat. The registered app will be shown in the plus (+) section of WeChat.
注册第三方app到微信主程序，注册后方可显示在微信聊天界面的附件添加面板中

ACTION_HANDLE_APP_UNREGISTER

static final java.lang.String ACTION_HANDLE_APP_UNREGISTER
Un-register the app to WeChat. The un-registered app will not be shown in the plus (+) section of Wechat.
反注册第三方app后，微信聊天界面的附件添加面板中将不会再出现该app
